org.odpi.openmetadata.viewservices.dataofficer.server.DataOfficerInstanceHandler
public class DataOfficerInstanceHandler extends OMVSServiceInstanceHandler
DataOfficerInstanceHandler retrieves information from the instance map for the view service instances. The instance map is thread-safe. Instances are added and removed by the DataOfficerAdmin class.
